{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773483496265,"sessionID":"ses_314277d05ffehFsuzTPHpcve3c","part":{"id":"prt_cebda9144001wKxHmHFxrvAJab","sessionID":"ses_314277d05ffehFsuzTPHpcve3c","messageID":"msg_cebda841a001zUL2HpvX7JhMVy","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01DuJcDMitoSMK7Xk3MTjWM8","tool":"read","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/token-cli/src/index.ts","limit":15,"offset":488},"output":"<path>/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/token-cli/src/index.ts</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>488:   WOMBO COMBO! Parallel feature development with AI agents.\n489: \n490: Commands:                        (alias)\n491:   init                           (i)     Generate .wombo-combo/config.json in the current project\n492:   launch                         (l)     Launch a wave of agents to implement features\n493:   resume                         (r)     Resume a previously stopped wave\n494:   status                         (s)     Show the status of the current wave\n495:   verify                         (v)     Run build verification on completed agents\n496:   merge                          (m)     Merge verified branches into the base branch\n497:   retry                          (re)    Retry a failed agent\n498:   abort                          (a)     Kill a single running agent (--requeue to return to queue)\n499:   logs                           (lo)    Pretty-print agent logs for a feature\n500:   cleanup                        (c)     Remove all wave worktrees and multiplexer sessions\n501:   history                        (h)     List/view past wave results (stored in .wombo-combo/history/)\n502:   tasks                          (t)     Manage tasks file (see below; 'features' also accepted)\n\n(Showing lines 488-502 of 1169. Use offset=503 to continue.)\n</content>","title":"src/index.ts","metadata":{"preview":"  WOMBO COMBO! Parallel feature development with AI agents.\n\nCommands:                        (alias)\n  init                           (i)     Generate .wombo-combo/config.json in the current project\n  launch                         (l)     Launch a wave of agents to implement features\n  resume                         (r)     Resume a previously stopped wave\n  status                         (s)     Show the status of the current wave\n  verify                         (v)     Run build verification on completed agents\n  merge                          (m)     Merge verified branches into the base branch\n  retry                          (re)    Retry a failed agent\n  abort                          (a)     Kill a single running agent (--requeue to return to queue)\n  logs                           (lo)    Pretty-print agent logs for a feature\n  cleanup                        (c)     Remove all wave worktrees and multiplexer sessions\n  history                        (h)     List/view past wave results (stored in .wombo-combo/history/)\n  tasks                          (t)     Manage tasks file (see below; 'features' also accepted)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"time":{"start":1773483496262,"end":1773483496265}}}}
