{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483659779,"sessionID":"ses_314277d05ffehFsuzTPHpcve3c","part":{"id":"prt_cebdca08500160iSK3KA6aZ2zo","sessionID":"ses_314277d05ffehFsuzTPHpcve3c","messageID":"msg_cebdc92cf0018gIAz3U381IY4n","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nAdd a `woco usage` CLI command to the wombo-combo agent orchestration system that displays aggregated token usage statistics from `.wombo-combo/usage.jsonl`. The command supports grouping by task/quest/model/provider/harness, date range filtering, and table or JSON output format.\n\n## Instructions\n\n- Feature ID: `token-cli`, Branch: `feature/token-cli`, Base: `main`\n- Use conventional commits with scope `token-cli`\n- Commit after each logical unit of work, do NOT squash, do NOT push\n- Command options: `--by task|quest|model|provider|harness` (default: total), `--since <ISO date>`, `--until <ISO date>`, `--format table|json` (default: table)\n- Table output: aligned columns showing group key, input tokens, output tokens, cache read, cache write, total\n- JSON output: raw aggregation result\n- Register in help text and schema\n- Must run `bun run build` to verify everything works before considering done\n- Always use `bun dev` not global binary when testing\n- No external CLI frameworks - arg parsing is hand-rolled in index.ts\n- Do NOT modify `tasks` directory (orchestrator handles that)\n- Do NOT push to remote (orchestrator handles that)\n\n## Discoveries\n\n- Token usage data is persisted in `.wombo-combo/usage.jsonl` as JSONL (one JSON per line), managed by `src/lib/token-usage.ts`\n- The `UsageRecord` type is defined in `src/lib/token-collector.ts` with fields: task_id, quest_id, model, provider, harness, input_tokens, output_tokens, cache_read, cache_write, reasoning_tokens, total_tokens, cost, timestamp, etc.\n- `GroupableField` type maps CLI values: task→task_id, quest→quest_id, model→model, provider→provider, harness→harness\n- The existing `token-usage.ts` already has all aggregation functions needed: `loadUsageRecords`, `filterByDateRange`, `groupBy`, `totalUsage`\n- Output follows a pattern using `output()` from `src/lib/output.ts` which handles text/json/toon formats\n- Commands follow a pattern: export interface for options, export async function `cmd*`, formatting helpers with ANSI codes\n- Schema registry in `src/lib/schema.ts` uses `COMMAND_REGISTRY` array of `CommandDef` objects\n- Shell completions (bash/zsh/fish) are generated in `src/commands/completion.ts` as template strings\n- The `--format` flag is specific to the usage command (table|json), separate from the global `--output` flag (text|json|toon)\n\n## Accomplished\n\n### Completed:\n1. **Created `src/commands/usage.ts`** — Full command implementation with table and JSON output, grouped and total views, date range filtering\n2. **Updated `src/index.ts`** — Added CLIArgs fields (usageBy, usageSince, usageUntil, usageFormat), parseArgs cases for --by/--since/--until/--format, command alias `us: \"usage\"`, help text with Usage Options section and examples, main() routing to cmdUsage\n3. **Updated `src/lib/schema.ts`** — Added usage command to COMMAND_REGISTRY with all flags defined\n4. **Committed** the core implementation (commit `d151f6a`)\n\n### In Progress:\n5. **Updating `src/commands/completion.ts`** — Bash completions are partially done (added alias resolution, --by/--format value completions, command list, describe list, per-command flags). **Zsh and Fish completions still need to be updated.**\n\n### Remaining:\n- Finish Zsh completion updates (add usage/us to commands list, alias resolution, flag value completions for --by/--format, per-command flags)\n- Finish Fish completion updates (add usage/us to top-level commands, add flag completions)\n- Commit the completion changes\n- Run `bun run build` and fix any errors\n- Verify build passes\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n- **`src/commands/usage.ts`** — NEW: The usage command implementation (table/JSON output, grouping, date filtering)\n- **`src/index.ts`** — MODIFIED: Added CLIArgs fields, parseArgs, alias, help text, routing\n- **`src/lib/schema.ts`** — MODIFIED: Added usage CommandDef to COMMAND_REGISTRY\n- **`src/commands/completion.ts`** — IN PROGRESS: Bash partially done, Zsh and Fish not yet updated\n- **`src/lib/token-usage.ts`** — READ: Contains all aggregation functions (loadUsageRecords, filterByDateRange, groupBy, totalUsage, UsageTotals, GroupableField)\n- **`src/lib/token-collector.ts`** — READ: UsageRecord type definition\n- **`src/lib/output.ts`** — READ: output(), outputError(), OutputFormat type\n- **`src/commands/history.ts`** — READ: Used as pattern reference for command structure\n- **`AGENTS.md`** — READ: Project conventions and constraints","time":{"start":1773483659777,"end":1773483659777}}}
